An '''achievement gallery''' is a room in a [[player-owned house]] in which the player can display their various accomplishments. It can be created at level 80 [[Construction]] for {{Coins|200000}}. Only one achievement gallery can be built per player.

If the player uses an orange [[spicy stew]] to boost their Construction by 5 levels, it is possible to build an achievement gallery at level 75 Construction.

There are 6 [[hotspot]]s available:
*[[Adventure log space]]
*[[Altar space#Achievement Gallery|Altar space]]
*[[Boss lair space]]
*[[Display space]]
*[[Jewellery box space]]
*[[Quest list space]]

